title: Jim Carr wins Winnipeg South Centre for the Liberals
text:
In the end, Winnipeg’s most-watched race wasn’t much of a race at all.
With 46 polls reporting, former Winnipeg South Centre MP Lloyd Axworthy took the microphone at Liberal Jim Carr’s victory party and declared victory. He said Carr has so far won with roughly 60 per cent of the vote.
Carr is expected to speak at about 10 p.m.
